_sText:
This is just a re-release of a map I made a couple years back. I figure there may still be some fun left in this map for others.

-PULLED FROM README MADE 2 YEARS AGO-

Surf_Skyworld_Fire

The Orignal maker of "Surf_Skyworld" is unknown.
I (Olaf "ClanFever" Flesch) have made this map. The things I have done are:
Smoothen ramps
Make a hole in the triangle with a buyzone in the middle
A sun, and proper lighting
TMP's and M4's at bottom of surf.
A whole retexture
Optimizations
Fire replaces brokensurf, and "Clan Fever" above spawn.

This request was made by Fire.

Known Errors:
Hammer hates us all, and it has decided two surf plates shouldn't be even. This should not affect your surfing.
